{"tid":1899761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[ 百屌成材 ] 楊岳橋率領泛民主派，成功冼到保皇黨一仆一碌 ! !","createTime":"2020-02-26T20:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T21:59:05.000Z","uid":219007,"like":18,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cf49791d41ca30d0b78433eb9c8857a2297dba45","tid":1899761,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:33:19.000Z","msg":"當大家仲屌緊保皇黨個頭反對派錢，呢頭扮成功爭取...<br />\n其實成件事一切都係楊岳橋計劃之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRdUZHfzZbg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTRdUZHfzZbg&d=dKvfM97HALqNkq2vb6iplA2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=959aa69b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TRdUZHfzZbg</a><br />\n毓民踩場 - [ 立法會議員楊岳橋Alvin Yeung玩嘢 建制派唔識應對 ] <br />\n<br />\n聽毓民講返，原來成件事係咁:<br />\n本身成件議案題目係300億抗疫撥款，直到議案討論尾段，楊岳橋突然係會上提出37A臨時動議要求討讑派錢一萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先，成件議題係300億抗疫撥款，派錢一萬根本唔關呢個議案範疇事，討論亦已經到左尾段，係呢係時候提出37A臨時動議已經拉唔到布，加上依家37A拉布空間有限，而最後九成泛民投贊成票亦證明佢地其實唔係反對呢個議案。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n按照常理，唔關事既留待另外一個議案再討論，所以保皇黨否決AY動議好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係呢個時候保皇黨中大伏了</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當保皇黨否決AY動議要求討讑派錢一萬，泛民就指保皇黨係反對派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而保皇黨就繼續早收三日風，扮成功爭取派錢，咁樣只會顯得佢哋反對派錢之後扮支持派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，前言不對後語<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家泛民媒體Page就起勢咁造圖、開街站宣傳保皇黨係反對派錢，前言不對後語<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保皇黨去到呢一刻先如夢初醒，原來自己俾人冼左獲金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁鋪水洗都唔清<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">楊岳橋老屈成功，KO建制派 ! ! </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保皇狗，你都有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c105b50960c3261ca5bb4a5f52e7a5cf82c723","tid":1899761,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:35:52.000Z","msg":"保皇黨反對派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5537be34b9b0ab2248916f088a5778dad784ead3","tid":1899761,"uid":73907,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:36:46.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係好睇得明 但好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a603be33e61c878e9273b2ac6d04235aa58e4e","tid":1899761,"uid":88743,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:39:35.000Z","msg":"又通宵開鬼po<br />\n楊岳橋老屈成功？ 邊撚度屈<br />\n事實真係否決左喎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五毛 拉</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"ebac2a84edb4cc2d10bc95bfc447b3a15a7f4544","tid":1899761,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:42:34.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n淨係識玩政治叻有閪用咩<br />\n手足比人濫捕鳩告嗰陣公文袋去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2014e6125db34ed69d253888b55be41a726a83dd","tid":1899761,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"d4a603be33e61c878e9273b2ac6d04235aa58e4e","tid":1899761,"uid":88743,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:39:35.000Z","msg":"又通宵開鬼po<br />\n楊岳橋老屈成功？ 邊撚度屈<br />\n事實真係否決左喎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五毛 拉</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:45:43.000Z","msg":"即係呢一刻全世界的定咗聽日係食麵，今日去食飯<br />\n<br />\n而家食飯嘅時間楊岳橋突然提出討論食麵落唔落醋<br />\n<br />\n咁正常嚟講應該聽日先食麵，咁咪留返聽日先講<br />\n<br />\n所以建制派就否決佢臨時動議<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候泛民就大事宣揚話建制派反對食麵落醋<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋擺明陰建制派一鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5938113c3fa55a43f0f2cc945ae237b4857266c7","tid":1899761,"uid":232927,"like":5,"dislik